cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper discusses the development of natural language processing applications for multiple languages, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions information retrieval (cs.IR) and text mining (cs.LG) as related fields. The use of self-training tools and the need for language resources suggest a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL).
